\pard\sa160\fs26 \b About this service\b0\par
\pard\sa160\fs22 DYAR provides allied health under NDIS Therapeutic Supports \u8212? Occupational Therapy, Psychology, Counselling, and Speech Pathology. All clinicians are AHPRA-registered (or ACA / PACFA for counselling), insured, and follow evidence-based practice. We work in clinic, home, school, and community settings.\par
\pard\sa120\fs22 \b NDIS funding categories\b0\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\fs22 \bullet  Capacity Building \u8212? Improved Daily Living (Therapeutic Supports)\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\fs22 \bullet  Capacity Building \u8212? Improved Health and Wellbeing (where applicable)\par
\pard\sa160\fs26 \b How to submit this referral\b0\par
\pard\sa160\fs22 Complete the form below and either: (a) submit via the DYAR website form at dyar.com.au, (b) email it to hello@dyar.com.au, or (c) call DYAR on 0470 540 306 and one of our team will complete the form with you over the phone. DYAR will acknowledge every referral within 2 business days.\par
